          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md group/btn _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" data-testid="action-bar-copy" aria-label="Copy"><div class="relative text-text-500 group-hover/btn:text-text-100"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="absolute top-0 left-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></button></div><div class="flex items-center"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-test-render-count="2"><div class="group" style="height: auto; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="contents"><div data-is-streaming="false" class="group relative relative pb-3" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Perfect! Here's your tailored step-by-step plan to get <strong>jurisnair.com</strong> live — free, no coding needed.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">🗺️ Your Website Plan</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Best free platform for you: Google Sites</strong> <em>(free, beginner-friendly, connects to your GoDaddy domain)</em></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Alternatively, <strong>Framer</strong> or <strong>Wix</strong> work too, but Google Sites is the simplest to connect with GoDaddy for free.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Step-by-Step Guide</h2>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Step 1 — Build Your Site on Google Sites</h3>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://sites.google.com/">sites.google.com</a> and sign in with a Google account (use <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="mailto:sanjeev@jurisnair.com">sanjeev@jurisnair.com</a> if it's a Gmail, or create a free Google account)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>"+ Blank"</strong> to start a new site</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Create the following <strong>4 pages</strong>: Home/About, Services, Blog, Contact</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add your content — name, description of legal &amp; consulting services, contact details</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">For the <strong>Contact Form</strong>, insert a linked Google Form (Insert → Forms)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">For <strong>Blog</strong>, use the "Text + Image" layout per post, or link to a free Blogger account</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Step 2 — Connect Your GoDaddy Domain</h3>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">In Google Sites, go to <strong>Settings (⚙️) → Custom Domain</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Type <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">www.jurisnair.com</code> and follow the verification steps</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Google will give you a <strong>CNAME record</strong> (looks like: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">google-site-verification=xxxxx</code>)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Log in to <strong>GoDaddy → My Products → DNS Settings</strong> for jurisnair.com</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add the CNAME record Google provides</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Wait 15–30 minutes for it to go live ✅</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Step 3 — Polish Before You Publish</h3>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add a <strong>professional photo or logo</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Write a short <strong>bio/About section</strong> (I can help draft this!)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">List your <strong>key services</strong> clearly (e.g., Legal Advisory, Corporate Consulting)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add your email <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">sanjeev@jurisnair.com</code> to the Contact page</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Step 4 — Publish</h3>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click the <strong>Publish</strong> button in Google Sites</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your site will be live at <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="http://www.jurisnair.com/">www.jurisnair.com</a></strong> 🎉</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">⚠️ A Few Things to Know</h2>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Google Sites is <strong>completely free</strong> — no hosting fees</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your GoDaddy domain renewal (~$15/yr) is the only cost</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Google Sites doesn't support a professional email inbox — for that you'd need Google Workspace (~$6/mo), but you can still <em>display</em> <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="mailto:sanjeev@jurisnair.com">sanjeev@jurisnair.com</a> as a contact address for free</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Would you like me to help you <strong>draft the content</strong> for any of the pages (Home, Services, etc.)? I can write professional copy for a legal &amp; consulting firm right here! 🖊️</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
