ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">That's a great initiative! However, I need to be upfront with you about something important.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>I can't directly log into websites or click buttons on your behalf</strong> — I don't have the ability to access Google Sites, GoDaddy, or any external platform directly, even with your credentials.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">What I <em>can</em> do very well is:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Build your entire website's content and design</strong> right here, and give you a ready-to-paste version</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Draft all page content</strong> (Home/About, Services, Blog, Contact) professionally tailored for a legal &amp; consulting firm</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Guide you live</strong>, step by step, with exact clicks and screenshots described, so it takes you minimal effort</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Here's what I propose as the <strong>easiest path for you:</strong></p></div></div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Also — to write accurate content for your site, could you share a few quick details?</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your <strong>full name</strong> and <strong>designation/title</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">A <strong>brief description</strong> of your services (e.g., areas of law, type of consulting)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your <strong>location/city</strong></li>
</ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
