ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Great call! Keeping it as <strong>Juris Nair</strong> gives it a more firm/brand feel rather than a personal one — much more professional and scalable if you ever expand the practice. Let me update that now.</p></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Edited 5 files, read a file</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Edited 5 files, read a file</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Done! All references to "Sanjeev Nair" have been replaced. The site now presents consistently as <strong>Juris Nair</strong> — clean, firm-branded, and professional throughout.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Whenever you're ready to add your name back (or a team page), that's an easy update. Any other changes you'd like before uploading to GoDaddy?</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="group/artifact-block relative flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300/15 hover:border-border-200"><button type="button" class="absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer rounded-[inherit] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-inset focus-visible:ring-accent-200" aria-label="Index. Open artifact."></button><div class="artifact-block-cell flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M67.84,92.61,25.37,128l42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,1-7.68,9.22l-48-40a6,6,0,0,1,0-9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,1,7.68,9.22Zm176,30.78-48-40a6,6,0,1,0-7.68,9.22L230.63,128l-42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,0,7.68,9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,0,0-9.22Zm-81.79-89A6,6,0,0,0,154.36,38l-64,176A6,6,0,0,0,94,221.64a6.15,6.15,0,0,0,2,.36,6,6,0,0,0,5.64-3.95l64-176A6,6,0,0,0,162.05,34.36Z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-4 min-w-0 flex-