ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">No worries at all! Here's exactly what to do, step by step — no coding knowledge needed.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">📥 Step 1 — Download the File</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click the <strong>index.html</strong> file link above (the one Claude shared)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">It will open in your browser — that's normal!</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Press <strong>Ctrl + S</strong> (Windows) or <strong>Cmd + S</strong> (Mac) to save it</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Save it to somewhere easy to find, like your <strong>Desktop</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Name it exactly: <strong>index.html</strong></li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">🌐 Step 2 — Log in to GoDaddy</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="http://www.godaddy.com/">www.godaddy.com</a></strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Sign In</strong> (top right)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Enter your GoDaddy credentials</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">📂 Step 3 — Find Your File Manager</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Once logged in, click <strong>My Products</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Look for <strong>Web Hosting</strong> and click <strong>Manage</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">This opens your hosting control panel (called <strong>cPanel</strong>)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Look for an icon called <strong>File Manager</strong> and click it</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">⬆️ Step 4 — Upload Your File</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">In File Manager, click on the folder called <strong>public_html</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click the <strong>Upload</strong> button at the top</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Select your <strong>index.html</strong> file from your Desktop</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Wait for it to upload — it takes just a few seconds</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">✅ Step 5 — Check Your Website</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Open a new browser tab</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Type <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="http://www.jurisnair.com/">www.jurisnair.com</a></strong> and press Enter</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your website should be live! 🎉</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">⚠️ One Important Thing</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Before Step 3, I need to confirm — <strong>do you have a Web Hosting plan on GoDaddy?</strong> Owning a domain and having hosting are two separate things on GoDaddy.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Could you log in to GoDaddy and tell me what you see under <strong>My Products</strong>? I'll guide you from there!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
