ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">That's actually a good starting point! GoDaddy has set up a <strong>"Coming Soon" page</strong> for jurisnair.com which means your domain is live and working.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Now we have two things we can do:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5"></div></div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">My strong recommendation is <strong>Switch to a Full Website</strong> — because:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The Coming Soon page is just a placeholder — visitors can't learn about your services or contact you</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">GoDaddy's free plan allows a full website with multiple sections</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">All the content we've already built (Services, About, Contact, Blog) can go in there</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">What do you see on screen — is there a <strong>"Make the switch to a full website"</strong> or <strong>"Learn More"</strong> link? Click that if yes! 🙂</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
