<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Can you tell me exactly what you see on the <strong>Pages</strong> settings screen? For example:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
