ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Perfect! That's exactly what we need. Now do this:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Activate GitHub Pages</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Under <strong>"Build and deployment"</strong> you'll see a section called <strong>"Source"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">There's a dropdown below it — it likely says <strong>"Deploy from a branch"</strong> — leave that as is</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Below that you'll see <strong>"Branch"</strong> with a dropdown that says <strong>"None"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click that <strong>"None"</strong> dropdown and select <strong>"main"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">A second dropdown will appear showing <strong>"/ (root)"</strong> — leave that as is</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click the <strong>"Save"</strong> button</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Then:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Wait <strong>2-3 minutes</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Open a new tab and go to <strong>sanjeevnair75.github.io</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your Juris Nair website should be live! 🎉</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Tell me what you see!</strong> 😊</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
