ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Perfect! Now let's tell GoDaddy to point to GitHub.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Part 2 — Update GoDaddy DNS Settings</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Open a new tab and go to <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="http://www.godaddy.com/">www.godaddy.com</a></strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Sign in to your account</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>"My Products"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Next to <strong>jurisnair.com</strong> click <strong>"DNS"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">You'll see a table with DNS records — look for a record of type <strong>"CNAME"</strong> that says <strong>"www"</strong> in the Name column</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click the <strong>pencil/edit icon ✏️</strong> next to it</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">In the <strong>"Value"</strong> or <strong>"Points to"</strong> field — delete whatever is there and type exactly: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">sanjeevnair75.github.io</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>"Save"</strong></li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Then also add these 4 records — look for an <strong>"Add New Record"</strong> button and add each one:</p>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Type</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Name</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Value</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">A</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">@</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">185.199.108.153</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">A</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">@</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">185.199.109.153</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">A</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">@</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">185.199.110.153</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">A</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">@</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">185.199.111.153</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<blockquote class="ml-2 border-l-4 border-border-300/10 pl-4 text-text-300">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">⏳ Once saved, it can take <strong>10-30 minutes</strong> for the domain to fully connect!</p>
</blockquote>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Tell me once you've saved all the records!</strong> 😊</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
