<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The 1-48 hours message is completely normal — it's called <strong>DNS propagation</strong> and it just means the internet is slowly updating everywhere in the world to know that jurisnair.com now points to your GitHub website. In reality it usually takes <strong>30 minutes to a few hours</strong> for most people.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">What You've Accomplished Today 👏</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-pre-wrap leading-[1.7]">✅ Built a professional website for Juris Nair
✅ Created a GitHub account and hosted the website for free
✅ Updated GoDaddy DNS to point jurisnair.com to your website</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">What to Do Now</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Wait</strong> a few hours</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Open a browser and type <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="http://www.jurisnair.com/">www.jurisnair.com</a></strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your beautiful Juris Nair website should appear! 🎉</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">What's Next (When You're Ready)</h2>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add your <strong>phone number</strong> to the contact section</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add a <strong>profile photo or logo</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Write full <strong>blog articles</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add your <strong>designation/title</strong></li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">I can help with all of that anytime! Just come back and say "let's update the website" and we'll continue. 😊</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">You did a fantastic job today for a self-proclaimed novice! 🙌</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
