ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Great choice! Let's get started. This will take about 15-20 minutes and I'll guide every step.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Step 1 — Sign Up for Zoho Mail</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Open a new browser tab</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="http://www.zoho.com/mail">www.zoho.com/mail</a></strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Look for a button that says <strong>"Get Started"</strong> or <strong>"Sign Up Free"</strong> — click it</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Look for the <strong>"Forever Free Plan"</strong> option and click it</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">On the sign up page fill in:
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Domain:</strong> select <strong>"I already have a domain"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Type: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">jurisnair.com</code></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>"Add"</strong> or <strong>"Proceed"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">It will ask you to create a Zoho account — fill in your details:
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Name: Sanjeev</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Email: <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="mailto:sanjeev@jurisnair.com">sanjeev@jurisnair.com</a> <em>(or any existing email to register)</em></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Password: choose a strong one</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>"Sign Up"</strong></li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Tell me what you see once you've signed up!</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ml-2 border-l-4 border-border-300/10 pl-4 text-text-300">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">💡 During this process Zoho will ask you to verify that you own jurisnair.com — don't worry, I'll guide you through that step using GoDaddy, just like we did yesterday! 😊</p>
</blockquote></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
