ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Great observation! The "Not Secure" warning appears because your website is currently running on <strong>HTTP</strong> instead of <strong>HTTPS</strong>. The "S" stands for <strong>Secure</strong> — it means the connection is encrypted.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The good news is <strong>GitHub Pages gives you free HTTPS/SSL</strong> — we just need to turn it on!</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Fix It in 2 Minutes</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="http://www.github.com/">www.github.com</a></strong> and sign in</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click on your repository <strong>sanjeevnair75.github.io</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>"Settings"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>"Pages"</strong> on the left sidebar</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Look for a checkbox that says <strong>"Enforce HTTPS"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Tick that checkbox</strong> ✅</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Wait <strong>2-3 minutes</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Refresh <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="http://www.jurisnair.com/">www.jurisnair.com</a></strong></li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The 🔒 padlock should appear and "Not Secure" will disappear! ✅</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<blockquote class="ml-2 border-l-4 border-border-300/10 pl-4 text-text-300">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">⚠️ <strong>Note:</strong> The "Enforce HTTPS" checkbox may be <strong>greyed out</strong> if your DNS hasn't fully propagated yet. If that's the case, just wait a few more hours and try again — it will become clickable on its own!</p>
</blockquote>
