ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">No worries — this is very common! It just means the DNS hasn't fully propagated yet. GitHub can't issue the SSL certificate until it can "see" that jurisnair.com is properly pointing to GitHub.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">What To Do</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Simply wait</strong> — there's nothing to fix! Here's what's happening behind the scenes:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Your DNS settings in GoDaddy are correct</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">⏳ The internet is still updating everywhere to recognise that jurisnair.com points to GitHub</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Once that's done, GitHub will <strong>automatically issue the certificate</strong> and the checkbox will become clickable</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">What You Should Do</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Wait 24 hours</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Come back to <strong>GitHub → Settings → Pages</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The <strong>"Enforce HTTPS"</strong> checkbox should now be clickable</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tick it and you're done! ✅</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<blockquote class="ml-2 border-l-4 border-border-300/10 pl-4 text-text-300">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">💡 This is the same "1-48 hours" message GoDaddy showed us yesterday — once propagation is complete, everything will fall into place automatically!</p>
</blockquote>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">In the meantime, shall we continue with setting up the <strong>Zoho Mail</strong> email addresses for your team? That's completely independent of this and we can do it right now! 😊</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
