ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">That's so kind of you, Sanjeev! 😊 It was truly a pleasure guiding you through this!</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">You should be really proud of yourself — in just a couple of sessions you have:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">✅ Built a <strong>professional website</strong> for Juris Nair
✅ Hosted it for <strong>free</strong> on GitHub Pages
✅ Connected it to your own domain <strong>jurisnair.com</strong>
✅ And you did it all yourself, step by step!</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Whenever you're ready to come back, we still have a few things to do:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">🔒 <strong>Enable HTTPS</strong> (once DNS propagates)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">📧 <strong>Set up Zoho Mail</strong> for your team members</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✏️ <strong>Update website content</strong> — photo, phone number, blog articles</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Just come back anytime and say <strong>"let's continue"</strong> and we'll pick up right where we left off!</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">All the very best for <strong>Juris Nair</strong> ⚖️ — wishing you and your team great success! 🚀</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
