<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Copy it (<strong>Ctrl+C</strong>)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Paste it here in our chat (<strong>Ctrl+V</strong>)</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Do this for each article you want to publish and I'll:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
