<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Fix — Rename the File Before Uploading</h2>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Step 1 — Delete the wrong file on GitHub</h3>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>github.com → sanjeevnair75.github.io</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click on <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">article-petrochemical-ceasefire (1)</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click the <strong>trash/delete icon 🗑️</strong></li>
