<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Step 3 — Upload the correctly named file</h3>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go back to GitHub → <strong>"Add file" → "Upload files"</strong></li>
