<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">💡 The <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">(1)</code> happens when your computer already has a file with the same name — Windows automatically adds <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">(1)</code> to avoid duplicates. Always rename before uploading!</p>
