<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="http://www.jurisnair.com/">www.jurisnair.com</a></strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Scroll to the <strong>Insights section</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>"Read More"</strong> on the first article</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The full article should open with <strong>Sanjeev Nair</strong> as the author!</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Also do a <strong>hard refresh</strong> just in case:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Windows: <strong>Ctrl + Shift + R</strong></li>
