<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The striking <strong>4,83,000 vs 2,083</strong> bar comparison as the visual centrepiece</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your dark gold website theme</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Clean typographic layout matching your other articles</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">How to Save It as an Image</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Right click</strong> on the cover above</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Select <strong>"Save image as"</strong> or <strong>"Copy image"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Save it as <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">gstat-cover.png</code> on your Desktop</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Then come back and I'll build the full article page using it! 😊</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
